Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
write_path_list_summary(25.10)                  write_path_list_summary(25.10)

Name
       write_path_list_summary - Writes the Path List categorized summary into
       a text and/or CSV file

Syntax
       write_path_list_summary

       [-help]

       [-category <string>]

       [-compress]

       [-csv]

       -report <fileName>

       Writes the Path List categorized summary into a text and/or CSV file.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for each write_path_list_summary parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and  all  its  parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man write_path_list_summary

       -category <string>
              Specifies the category of paths to be stored into the CSV file.

       -compress
              Compresses the output file in the .gzip file format.

       -csv   Reports entries in the CSV format.

       -report <fileName>
              Specifies  the  name  of  the  output file in text, CSV, or com-
              pressed format.

Related Information
       The Timing Budgeting chapter of the Innovus User Guide document.

